dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contains the boundaries for Canada, Mexico, Greenland, the Dominican Republic, Cuba, Haiti, the Bahamas and Jamaica. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2. This shapefile provides a background layer for countries in North America. ESRI. (2014). North American Countries. ESRI. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/zz281cq9133.
